Interface ImmutableList<T>

  • Type Parameters:

    All Superinterfaces:

    public interface ImmutableList<T>
extends ImmutableCollection<T>, java.io.Serializable
    List, like java.util.List , but has no operation that changes the list. Only "read" operations are supplied.
    Author:
    Asher Stern
